[8.34, "o", "\r\n"]
[8.44, "o", "\u001b[2;90m"]
[8.59, "o", "<think>\r\n"]
[8.74, "o", "Okay, let's see. The video shows a first-person view\r\n"]
[8.89, "o", "from a vehicle's dashboard camera in a residential area.\r\n"]
[9.04, "o", "The car is stopped at an intersection, and the driver is\r\n"]
[9.19, "o", "waiting for a pedestrian to cross.\r\n"]
[9.34, "o", "\r\n"]
[9.49, "o", "Key elements:\r\n"]
[9.64, "o", "\u2022 Parked cars on both sides of the street\r\n"]
[9.79, "o", "\u2022 Pedestrian crossing the intersection\r\n"]
[9.94, "o", "\u2022 Clear sky, good visibility\r\n"]
[10.09, "o", "\u2022 Quiet residential neighborhood\r\n"]
[10.24, "o", "\r\n"]
[10.39, "o", "The main hazard is the pedestrian. The driver should stay\r\n"]
[10.54, "o", "alert for unexpected movements from parked cars \u2014 like a\r\n"]
[10.69, "o", "door opening or someone stepping out between vehicles.\r\n"]
[10.84, "o", "</think>\r\n"]
[10.94, "o", "\u001b[0m"]
[11.24, "o", "\r\n"]
[11.36, "o", "\u001b[1;37m\u2501\u2501\u2501 Analysis Result \u2501\u2501\u2501\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[11.48, "o", "\r\n"]
[11.6, "o", "\u001b[1;33m\u26a0\ufe0f  Hazards Identified:\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[11.72, "o", "  1. Pedestrian crossing intersection\r\n"]
[11.84, "o", "  2. Parked vehicles obstructing visibility\r\n"]
[11.96, "o", "  3. Potential for car doors opening unexpectedly\r\n"]
[12.08, "o", "\r\n"]
[12.2, "o", "\u001b[1;32m\u2705 Recommended Actions:\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[12.32, "o", "  \u2192 Wait for pedestrian to fully cross\r\n"]
[12.44, "o", "  \u2192 Proceed cautiously at low speed\r\n"]
[12.56, "o", "  \u2192 Monitor parked vehicles for movement\r\n"]
[12.68, "o", "  \u2192 Check blind spots before accelerating\r\n"]
[12.8, "o", "\r\n"]
